OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774246422
OL,3,CAspiring first-time buyers with
OL,4,Cstudent debt 'face #2,000 annual
OL,5,Csavings gap'
OL,7,FPeople who are saving up for a house
OL,8,Fdeposit are putting aside around
OL,9,F#2,000 per year less typically if they
OL,10,Fare still paying off a student loan,
OL,11,Fcompared with those without education
OL,12,Fdebts, according to research for a
OL,13,Fbank.
OL,15,FThe savings gap was highlighted by
OL,16,FBarclays, which found deposit savers
OL,17,Fwith outstanding student debt were
OL,18,Fputting away #310.00 per month on
OL,19,Faverage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774246422
OL,3,CAspiring first-time buyers with
OL,4,Cstudent debt 'face #2,000 annual
OL,5,Csavings gap'
OL,7,FPeople who were saving up but did not
OL,8,Fhave a student loan saved #473.70 per
OL,9,Fmonth ` or an extra #163.70, adding up
OL,10,Fto an additional #1,964.40 per year.
OL,12,FMore than two-fifths (44%) of people
OL,13,Fwith student loans said the debt makes
OL,14,Fit harder to be financially stable,
OL,15,Fwith 41% saying their repayments make
OL,16,Fit harder to save for a home,
OL,17,Faccording to the Barclays property
OL,18,Finsights report.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774246422
OL,3,CAspiring first-time buyers with
OL,4,Cstudent debt 'face #2,000 annual
OL,5,Csavings gap'
OL,7,FThe bank is also seeing signs in its
OL,8,Fown data that more first-time buyers
OL,9,Fare targeting homes at "nil rate"
OL,10,Fstamp duty thresholds below #300,000.
OL,11,FStamp duty applies in England and
OL,12,FNorthern Ireland, with separate
OL,13,Fproperty taxes in Scotland and Wales.
OL,15,FBarclays mortgage data shows that
OL,16,Fproperties priced at under #300,000
OL,17,Fmade up 68.5% of first-time buyer
OL,18,Fpurchases in February 2026, compared
OL,19,Fwith 60.9% in February 2025.
OL,26,@qD@XOUqD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30504
