CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774246422
OL,3,CAspiring first-time buyers with
OL,4,Cstudent debt 'face #2,000 annual
OL,5,Csavings gap'
OL,7,FJatin Patel, head of mortgages,
OL,8,Fsavings and insurance at Barclays,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Rising external costs are
OL,10,Freshaping how the UK approaches
OL,11,Fhomeownership.
OL,13,F"Student loan repayments are slowing
OL,14,Fdeposit saving for many aspiring
OL,15,Fbuyers, while volatile energy prices
OL,16,Fare forcing households to think much
OL,17,Fharder about the long-term running
OL,18,Fcosts of their homes."
OL,26,@qD@GOUuD@AOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774246422
OL,3,CAspiring first-time buyers with
OL,4,Cstudent debt 'face #2,000 annual
OL,5,Csavings gap'
OL,7,FMany mortgage lenders have increased
OL,8,Ftheir rates or withdrawn products in
OL,9,Frecent weeks. The conflict in the
OL,10,FMiddle East has led to changing
OL,11,Fexpectations for financial markets.
OL,12,FSwap rates, which are used by lenders
OL,13,Fto price mortgages, have increased.
OL,15,FMr Patel added: "Homeowners are
OL,16,Funderstandably concerned about rising
OL,17,Ffixed rates across the market, but
OL,18,Fit's important to remember that there
OL,19,Fare options available.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
