SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1774246422
OL,3,CAspiring first-time buyers with
OL,4,Cstudent debt 'face #2,000 annual
OL,5,Csavings gap'
OL,7,F"You can typically lock in a new rate
OL,8,F90 days before your end of term date
OL,9,Fwith your existing lender `-or up to
OL,10,Fsix months out if you are looking at
OL,11,Fmoving lenders. This can provide peace
OL,12,Fof mind for those who want to protect
OL,13,Fthemselves against short-term
OL,14,Fvolatility, whilst planning ahead."
OL,16,FA survey of 2,000 people across the UK
OL,17,Fwas carried out by Opinium Research
OL,18,Ffor Barclays in March.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@cO]
